For Snow automation, create an OAUTH registry entry:

    Create an OAuth API endpoint for external clients

1. If using postman to get token:  use this redirect URL: 
    https://oauth.pstmn.io/v1/callback
2. uncheck pulbic client
3. Client Type: Integration as a Service
4. Auth Scope: useraccount

In Postman:
Grant type: Authorization Token
Callback URL:  https://oauth.pstmn.io/v1/callback or check the box for authorize in header
Auth URL:  https://<instance>.service-now.com/oauth_auth.do
Access Token URL: https://<instance>.service-now.com/oauth_token.do
Client ID:  ••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••
Client Secret: ••••••••••
Scope: useraccount
State: benstate
Client Authentication: Send as Basic Auth
